{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Beacon",
    "url": "https://w3c.github.io/beacon/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "html": "On calling the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/beacon/#dom-navigator-sendbeacon\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigator-sendbeacon⑧\">sendBeacon()</a></code> method with <var>url</var> and\noptional <var>data</var>, the following steps must be run:",
      "rationale": "set",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>base</var> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-settings-object\">relevant settings object</a>’s\n    <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#api-base-url\" id=\"ref-for-api-base-url\">API base URL</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>origin</var> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-settings-object①\">relevant settings object</a>’s\n    <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-settings-object-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-settings-object-origin\">origin</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>parsedUrl</var> to the result of the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-parser\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-parser\">URL parser</a>\n    steps with <var>url</var> and <var>base</var>. If the algorithm\n    returns an error, or if <var>parsedUrl</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-scheme\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-scheme\">scheme</a> is not\n    \"http\" or \"https\", <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw\">throw</a> a\n    \"<code><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror\">TypeError</a></code></code>\" exception and terminate these\n    steps.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var>headerList</var> be an empty list."
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var>corsMode</var> be \"<code>no-cors</code>\"."
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>data</var> is not <code>null</code>:",
          "rationale": "set",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Set <var>transmittedData</var> and <var>contentType</var> to the\n        result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-bodyinit-extract\" id=\"ref-for-concept-bodyinit-extract\">extracting</a> <var>data</var>’s\n        byte stream with the <var>keepalive flag</var> set."
            },
            {
              "html": "If the amount of data that can be queued to be sent by\n        <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#request-keepalive-flag\" id=\"ref-for-request-keepalive-flag②\">keepalive</a> enabled requests is exceeded by the size of\n        <var>transmittedData</var> (as defined in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-http-network-or-cache-fetch\" id=\"ref-for-concept-http-network-or-cache-fetch①\">HTTP-network-or-cache fetch</a>),\n        set the return value to <code>false</code> and\n        terminate these steps."
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>contentType</var> is not null:\n        \n       <ul>\n        <li>Set <var>corsMode</var> to \"<code>cors</code>\".\n        </li><li>If <var>contentType</var> value is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#cors-safelisted-request-header\" id=\"ref-for-cors-safelisted-request-header\">CORS-safelisted request-header</a> value for the <code>Content-Type</code>\n          header, set <var>corsMode</var> to \"<code>no-cors</code>\".\n          \n        </li><li>Append a <code>Content-Type</code> header with value\n          <var>contentType</var> to <var>headerList</var>.\n       </li></ul>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Set the return value to <code>true</code>, return the\n  <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/beacon/#dom-navigator-sendbeacon\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigator-sendbeacon⑨\">sendBeacon()</a></code> call, and continue to run the following steps in\n  parallel:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>req</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request\">request</a>, initialized as\n        follows:</p>\n       <dl>\n        <dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-method\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-method\">method</a>\n        </dt><dd><code>POST</code>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-client\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-client\">client</a>\n        </dt><dd><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this②\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-settings-object\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-settings-object②\">relevant settings object</a>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-url\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-url\">url</a>\n        </dt><dd><var>parsedUrl</var>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-header-list\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-header-list\">header list</a>\n        </dt><dd><var>headerList</var>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-origin\">origin</a>\n        </dt><dd><var>origin</var>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#request-keepalive-flag\" id=\"ref-for-request-keepalive-flag④\">keepalive</a>\n        </dt><dd><code>true</code>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-body\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-body\">body</a>\n        </dt><dd><var>transmittedData</var>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-mode\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-mode\">mode</a>\n        </dt><dd><var>corsMode</var>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-request-credentials-mode\" id=\"ref-for-concept-request-credentials-mode\">credentials mode</a>\n        </dt><dd><code>include</code>\n        </dd><dt><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#request-initiator-type\" id=\"ref-for-request-initiator-type\">initiator type</a>\n        </dt><dd>\"<code>beacon</code>\"\n       </dd></dl>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-fetch\" id=\"ref-for-concept-fetch①\">Fetch</a> <var>req</var>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}